Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:00.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you change your clothes, nee-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:03.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We won't return here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:07.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take everything we need with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know, nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, nii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:23.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please become nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:26.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, nii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:31.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go, nee-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:34.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget your ticket and passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:39.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we can't go anywhere without them or pass through any place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's go, nii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:47.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:18.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. That's correct. That's what I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:19.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:24.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rock. Until next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:27.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock gave us an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:30.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those brats are from Dracula's homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Romanians.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Romanian!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:39.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, the Romanian\nmilitary in Kabul used to speak like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:40.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:44.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It gets harder to remember things with age.\NDon't worry about it, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:46.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:53.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}A pink shop or pink salon is a type of whore house
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:53.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant, I recall that Rowan, the owner of the pink\nshop on Lachada Street, was selling illegal videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:56.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did Rowan do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you clear this place out, Chang?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:43.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is a delicate meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:45.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If this is a date, I more then welcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:50.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can't enjoy a movie and drinks\nwhile stinking of blood, now can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:53.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Chang, I found out who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:59.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a very interesting story. How did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:05.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,we found the answer in Rowan's goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:07.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Pink Shop" Rowan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:12.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You invited him to your office? I bet he was scared to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He was about to shit his pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How unpleasant for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:26.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him about child pornography\nthat had Romanian twins in it or snuff videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:29.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He gave us 250 videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's unpleasant as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:37.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It took an entire night looking through\nthose 250 videos for fucked up perverts,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but then "bingo", we found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hansel and Gretel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:49.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what those brats were called in the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:56.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Brats sold onto the black market by institutions that couldn't\nafford them anymore after the Romanian revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Children of a dead dictator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:04.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Made into the toys of perverts and ending up as pig food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:08.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was meant to be those brats' fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:09.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How did they avoid it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:15.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots made them finish off their\nvictims as a form of amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:19.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Finishing off sacrificial lambs,\nnot much different from themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:26.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To survive, those brats desperately learned\nways to kill that pleased the perverts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One night after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:32.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And at some point, they just accepted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:37.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They turned their backs on the blue sky,\nand entered into the shadows of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They decided to become show dogs on video, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a horrible story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yet appropriate for our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:53.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I feel like I'm walking over a huge pile of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:56.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Morality" and "Justice" don't really suit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:07:00.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Words like that and what comes\nout of asses are surprisingly similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:07.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Having sympathy for those kids is on the same level\nas idiots who wield missiles and talk about peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:09.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I only told you what I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:14.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need justice. We just need profit and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:21.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After Rowan, it was easy.\NJust needed to follow the purchase routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:25.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So this is the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:29.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If one of his relatives had died,\nit would've been a great alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was just for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They can't possibly be disciplined.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:36.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They are trouble to everyone around\nthem and shit on them in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your men were hit by their wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,a line must be drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:48.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on god dammit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:53.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They should have just taken care of that bitch,\nbut the corpses just keep piling up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:54.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:57.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we end it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:04.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can make it look like we took care\nof the guys who messed with this city!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to take care of them\nwithout creating a bigger mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:18.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For a shrimp, you sure talk big to your boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But boss, they're too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:29.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I called those\ndamn brats here in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:33.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's about time to\nchange this city's color, Chang?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then there'd be no reason for the committee to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to bring us to war again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:44.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I like to call it a controlled conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The reason and motive will stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:49.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a justified war then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:52.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you were the type to say sugarcoated words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:55.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If they're the right words for an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:58.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you feed this "justice" to the dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:02.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Join me, or forget about this. It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:05.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:09.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose there's no reason to\nreport back to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:12.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing you can trust in this world is brute force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:16.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll get to see you as a gunman again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:18.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:25.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind being in gunfights, but since I have\nto maintain my reputation, it's a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:29.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and don't call me "babe"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant, Chang has agreed to the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:47.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, the Hong Kong Triad will be our allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:48.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:50.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please notify our comrade soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Immediate standby from 1905.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:57.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I predict Lesson 217, Case 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:58.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:10:00.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Immediate standby from 1905.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:04.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You predict a snatch mission\nwithin enemy combat territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:09.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}"Da" means yes in Russian
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:09.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Da. I predict chaos. It's a carnival in the city at the moment with all the bounty hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:15.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's better that it's lively, Kapitan. There's nothing better than the roar of gunfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:16.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:20.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, this is the only war that we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:30.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Palermo bosses have great\ninterest in this shithole of a city!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:37.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're on edge because I can't do a single thing out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:40.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:45.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do something right now,\nat the next officer's meeting, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:47.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Um, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:49.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:52.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But... those twins are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,T-Those punks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:18.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I-I told them never to come here. What are they here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We talked about it and decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:29.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}Borscht: a vegetable soup usually red in color from beet roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We decided that Borscht will be the main dish,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:36.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}They're referring to the order of the mob bosses being targeted
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:36.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll start with the macaroni.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:47.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't you f-fuck around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The macaroni has boiled over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:55.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,God damned brats! Do you wanna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've completely surrounded the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We await your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:22.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:23.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:26.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should lower your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:35.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The job has changed to a hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:45.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Contact Hotel Moscow. I want to make them owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, the cops are on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:52.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They blocked off the entrances to the central road.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:55.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like something has\nhappened with the Verrocchio family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:59.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, we won't get any of the\nbounty if we stay on the sidelines!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:02.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. Don't yell, Eda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we meeting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:07.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Joey's got a room at the Barkana Square. Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:11.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:14.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fuse got lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just wait for the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:24.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Comrades, the Verrocchio Family\nhas been attacked tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there will be no change of plan. Do everything as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From this moment, we begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Courageous comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:38.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,to us, Warrant Officer Sahalov and Corporal\NMenishof were irreplaceable comrades in arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:43.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We are the ones who should offer a light for their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:47.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With our lost comrade's souls,\nour guns become Goddesses of Vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:52.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}Kalashnikov refers to the Avtomat Kalashnikova 1947 or AK-47
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:52.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give them punishment through our AKs and\nrip their jaws open with 5.45mm rounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:04.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Chang, we have word from Hotel Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"The situation is dangerous, retreat from the location."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:10.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:13.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:14.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cho, get your pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:20.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}The Chinese on Chang's pistol is "tentei", or literally, "Heavenly King"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:21.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:40.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Great! You're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:45.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate, but we can't deal with you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:47.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Till next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That puts me at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:53.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The source is the Verrocchio family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:57.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Watsup is interrogating the Triad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:00.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our route's about to pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:03.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The carnival night is about to start. Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:05.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, it's a black Japanese sedan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:08.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we won't know it's them if they ditch the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:10.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares. Shoot anyone that passes by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:12.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't push.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:17.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Eda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:19.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I just noticed something's strange, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:23.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Don't hold out on me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:25.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:30.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The woman with the biggest grudge hasn't appeared yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:33.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:38.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right? If this was the real deal, it'd be weird if we weren't shut out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:40.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, where will those twins go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:45.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're not rational, but their target is Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:50.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The others were diversions...\nno, they were just in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:57.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If Balalaika mobilized the Visotniki\nto completely annihilate the twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:16:01.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Military people are all pragmatists. They won't move carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The twins will definitely hit a blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:09.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All these guys think they're deer hunting in Montana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:12.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those twins are more like coyotes, it won't be this easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:17.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If they fell for this kind of trap, they'd be six feet under by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:21.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For an uneducated girl, you sure are quick, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:27.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the fastest back-street to Hotel Moscow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:31.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Through Chalquam Market and\nstraight down Sautanam Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:36.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you're the uneducated one, you whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:38.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for your loss, Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:43.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I had known those kids were here,\NI would have brought more men.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:47.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to them, I have to walk home. It's just my luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:50.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I got rid of Watsup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you didn't want to give it to those greedy pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:57.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's off on a wild goose chase, till the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:16:59.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, just pay me back someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shrewd as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:04.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Things are going smooth over here, Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The first march is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming! It's their car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:25.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake. A black Japanese sedan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are the twins inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's tinted... I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? Blow it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:13.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did we get 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:18.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're not white!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're local brats, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:23.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, we missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Watsup is heading towards the south port.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:26.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:27.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, you damn punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll smoke those brats out! Fuck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were absolutely right, nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:39.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Making a fake for only 5,000 baht was a bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:42.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel a little sorry for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They said they were orphans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:45.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped, nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's kill or be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:49.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:52.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, nii-sama. It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's kill. Let's kill even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:58.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:19.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The team behind Charkwan Street\nhas spotted the hated enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They have engaged in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:21.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they move next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:25.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,East, just as predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Momentarily, they will be at Radoga Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:48.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Target is out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:51.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're moving along the course nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:57.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Team 3 has attacked once and has broken away\nfrom Radoga Point, moving toward Livinsk now.\NStanding by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:01.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Place a team on Hamipon Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:02.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:06.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leave only one spot on the floodgate. Notify all teams to fall back after engaging the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The main mission is to divert the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:13.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which team was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We did not deploy in that area yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that those are bounty hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Team captains, report.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Deal with those who interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:27.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa now, don't move you damn brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:31.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bad things will happen if you hang out around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:35.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when the entire city is on a manhunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:39.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and say your prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:45.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:49.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How much money is on our heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:50.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,80,000 dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:52.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:54.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a very good price.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:57.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:21:00.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have the money from Verrocchio's office here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:05.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind fighting you here,\nbut we still have something that we want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How does 100,000 sound for having not seen us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:12.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck around. We're not punks on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:14.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how about 150,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:16.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:20.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:23.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Revy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic, Eda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:31.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take it all. The 80,000, the 150,000, and their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:35.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We have confirmed the target's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:37.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Chinese from the Lagoon Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:39.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the sister from the Church of Violence is with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:41.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:44.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If necessary, crush them underfoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:20.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of rotten blood and soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are the same thing!
